<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c3">{وَإِذَا قِيلَ لَهُمُ ارْكَعُوا لَا يَرْكَعُونَ}</span> <span class="c2">(١)</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c5">قَالَ الْبُخَارِيُّ ج٦ص١٦٤:</span> قَالَ مُجَاهِدٌ: <span class="c3">{ارْكَعُوا}</span>: صَلُّوا.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c3">{لَا يَرْكَعُونَ}</span>: لَا يُصَلُّونَ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<hr>
<p class="hamesh">(١) [المرسلات: ٤٨]</p> </div>